  "title": "HR Recruitment Associate - Entry-Level, Training Provided #NKA",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Intern/Temp/Perm</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Orchard</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Drafting and posting of job advertisements to attract potential candidates</li><li>Screening, shortlisting and interviewing of candidates to determine suitability</li><li>Editing and reformatting of resumes</li><li>Arranging and preparing candidates for interviews</li><li>Administering of contracts signing and follow through on employee benefits</li><li>Identifying and initiating potential key accounts</li><li>Business development of current and new clients; ie sales appointments, telemarketing</li><li>Achieve monthly targets and quota</li><li>Any ad-hoc administrative duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Degree in any discipline</li><li>No experience required as training is provided</li><li>Strong penchant for challenges and collaboration</li><li>Enjoys meeting people and working in team-based environment</li><li>Possess high interest in sales and business development functions</li><li>Self-motivated and independent</li></ul><p>Ally<br />The Outsourcing Team<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA: 99C4599</p>",
